In the 2010 national budget, the department received an [[appropriation (law)|appropriation]] of 6,166.2 million [[South African rand|rand]], and had 730 employees.<ref>{{cite book |title=Estimates of National Expenditure 2010 |publisher=National Treasury |location=Pretoria |isbn=978-0-621-39079-7 |date=17 February 2010 |chapter=Vote 14: Basic Education |url=http://www.treasury.gov.za/documents/national%20budget/2010/ene/default.aspx |chapterurl=http://www.treasury.gov.za/documents/national%20budget/2010/ene/vote14.pdf |accessdate=30 August 2010}}</ref>
