'''Racial nationalism''' is an [[ideology]] that advocates a [[Race (human categorization)|racial]] definition of [[national identity]]. Racial nationalism seeks to preserve a given race through policies such as banning [[Miscegenation|race mixing]] and the [[immigration]] of other races.
