'''Secure Network''' is a small research and consulting company focusing on [[Information Security]] based in [[Milano]], [[Italy]] and [[London]], [[United Kingdom]]. Besides having notability in [[Italy]],<ref>http://www.eurogroup.biz/web/canali-tematici/ict-internet/approfondimenti/LUCCHETTI-DIGITALI-DA-800-MILIONI_1390_4.jsp</ref> it received international exposure<ref>http://howto.techworld.com/mobile-wireless/2622/case-study-bluebag-finds-bluetooth-flaws/</ref><ref>http://www.infoworld.com/t/networking/bluebag-pc-sniffs-out-bluetooth-flaws-798</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.governmentsecurity.org/forum/index.php?showtopic=22577 |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2009-11-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110718143211/http://www.governmentsecurity.org/forum/index.php?showtopic=22577 |archivedate=2011-07-18 |df= }}</ref> with a research project on [[Bluetooth]] security (co-sponsored by [[F-Secure]]) codenamed BlueBag, which has been also selected for the [[Black Hat Briefings]] conference 2006 in [[Las Vegas Valley|Las Vegas]].<ref>http://www.tomshardware.com/news/blackhat2006-bluebag-bluetooth,3264.html</ref>
In 2009, it also organized [http://www.seacure.it SEaCURE.IT], the first international technical security conference ever held in Italy.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.smau.it/article/articleview/1576/1/ |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2009-11-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100213114635/http://www.smau.it/article/articleview/1576/1/ |archivedate=2010-02-13 |df= }}</ref><ref>http://www.bitcity.it/news/10632/seacure-it-focus-sulla-sicurezza-a-smau-2009.html</ref><ref>http://www.impresacity.it/speciali/2009/smau-milano-2009/dettaglio.php?q=__145_0_seacure-it-secure-network-porta-la-sicurezza-a-smau.html</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.datamanager.it/cms/view/sezioni_web/sicurezza/seacure_it_i_guru_della_sicurezza_a_smau_2009/s151/c81994 |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2009-11-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20110722031300/http://www.datamanager.it/cms/view/sezioni_web/sicurezza/seacure_it_i_guru_della_sicurezza_a_smau_2009/s151/c81994 |archivedate=2011-07-22 |df= }}</ref>
